longBusinessSummary: Nosa Plugs AB, a medical technology company, manufactures and sells intranasal breathing products primarily in Europe and North America. Its products include NOSA plugs, such as NOSA odor control products for odor protection; NOSA microbial control products to reduce the exposure of viruses and bacteria by inhalation through the nose; and NOSA allergy filter that filters harmful airborne particles, such as pollen, mites, dust, and mold. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
